lead_paragraph: After getting a rude introduction to the NFL after losing their first 10 games as rookies in 2014, Derek Carr and Khalil Mack have put the Oakland Raiders at the top of the AFC just two years later.

headline.print_headline: Mack, Carr Rally Raiders to 35-32 Win Over Panthers
